      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This driver-focused example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed cooling system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power delivery. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment. The chassis is enhanced with Bilstein B6 dampers and poly-bushing upgrades for sharpened turn-in response. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain and suspension geometry remain dialed-in for peak performance.",
