      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. Finished in a deep metallic charcoal, the exterior maintains a brilliant luster, showing only minor, expected stone peppering on the front fascia from highway travel. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the premium leather seats are free of punctures or stains, showing only light softening on the driver-side bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium audio system and ice-cold dual-zone climate control, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is robust\u2014the engine idles smoothly, and the transmission delivers crisp, confident shifts. It has been strictly maintained with synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the tires still have approximately 70% tread life remaining. While there is a small, professionally touched-up scratch near the rear wheel well, the car presents beautifully and drives with the tightness of a much newer model. A complete service history is available for your peace of mind.",
